<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A <db:link xlink:href="qt3drender-qdepthtest.xml">QDepthTest</db:link> class is used to enable depth testing with a given depth test function. The depth test enables writing fragment color values when the depth test passes, and reject fragments which fail the test. The depth test uses the depth function to test the fragments depth value to the value against z-buffer. If the underlying surface does not have z-buffer, then <db:link xlink:href="qt3drender-qdepthtest.xml">QDepthTest</db:link> does nothing.</db:para>
